/dstatus.en-us: Display license information for installed product keys.
/dstatus.zh-cn: 显示当前已安装产品密钥的许可证信息
/dstatus.zh-tw: 顯示當前已安裝產品密鑰的許可證信息

/dstatusall.en-us: Display license information for installed licenses.
/dstatusall.zh-cn: 显示当前已安装的所有许可证信息
/dstatusall.zh-tw: 顯示當前已安裝的所有許可證信息

/unpkey:XXXXX.en-us: Uninstall a product key with the last five digits of it.
/unpkey:XXXXX.zh-cn: 卸载已安装的产品密钥（最后5位）
/unpkey:XXXXX.zh-tw: 卸載已安裝的產品密鑰（最後5位）

/inpkey:XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX.en-us: Install a product key with user-provided product key.

/sethst:@HOST@.en-us: Set a KMS host name with user-provided host name.

/setprt:@PORT@.en-us: Set a KMS port with user-provided port number.
/setprt:@PORT@.zh-cn: 设置 KMS 主机端口
/setprt:@PORT@.zh-tw: 設置 KMS 主機端口

/remhst.en-us: Remove KMS host name and sets port to default.
